Detailed Description

Indicates a latitude and longitude in semicircles. /.

Indicates a 2D position in semicircles, where 2^31 //! semicircles equal 180 degrees. North latitudes and East //! longitudes are indicated with positive numbers; South latitudes //! and West longitudes are indicated with negative numbers. All //! positions are given in WGS-84.
